rows.label: qst701915_msg0002
rows.name: Maybe I'll grab a bite before we leave.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0101
rows.name: Why did you choose me as leader?

rows.label: qst701915_msg0102
rows.name:
As a representative of the
resistance, I'll carry out
the mission properly, but...

rows.label: qst701915_msg0103
rows.name:
If I'm busy being the leader,
I'll have less time to eat.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0201
rows.name:
Now that the mission is over,
I want to enjoy some good
drinks and a full meal.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0202
rows.name:
But the Lieutenant is glaring
at me, so I'm holding back.

rows.label: qst701915_msg0203
rows.name:
I should have eaten my
fill of Praan in Fons Maim
when I had the chance.
